OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FThe number of active taxi drivers in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland has dropped to 5,719
OL,8,Fwhile a proposed legislative change
OL,9,Fcould increase fares and put firms out
OL,10,Fof business, a Stormont committee has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FThe Department of Infrastructure has
OL,14,Fproposed changing taxi operator
OL,15,Flicensing regulation following court
OL,16,Fcases in England and Wales.
