OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FAppearing before the Stormont
OL,7,FInfrastructure Committee, Stephen
OL,8,FAnton of the Licensed Taxi Operators
OL,9,FAssociation outlined that in 2014
OL,10,Fthere were nearly 16,000 taxi licences
OL,11,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,13,FHe said the number of taxi licences in
OL,14,FDecember 2023 was 7,500.
OL,16,FHowever, he said that is simply the
OL,17,Fnumber of licences, not the number of
OL,18,Factive taxi drivers.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/12
