OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,F"In order to be a licensed taxi driver
OL,7,Foperating, you have to be affiliated
OL,8,Fto a taxi operator, and in January of
OL,9,Fthis year there were 5,719 affiliated
OL,10,Fdrivers, and we know from our own
OL,11,Fexperience that on any given week
OL,12,Faround 80-85% of the taxi drivers who
OL,13,Fare working are actually out working
OL,14,Fif you take out holidays and sickness
OL,15,Fand so on," he told the committee.
OL,17,F"So on any given week you are looking
OL,18,Fat around 5,000 drivers operating
OL,19,Facross the whole of Northern Ireland."
