OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FMr Anton raised concern about the
OL,7,Fimpact of a proposed legislative
OL,8,Fchange which he said, if implemented,
OL,9,Fcould increase fares by 20% and has
OL,10,Fthe potential to close operators.
OL,12,FThe proposed change to the Taxi
OL,13,FOperators Licensing Regulations
OL,14,F(Northern Ireland) 2012 follows the
OL,15,Foutcome of a number of court
OL,16,Fproceedings in England and Wales.
