OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FHe said while on paper it looks like a
OL,7,Fsimple change, the status of a taxi
OL,8,Foperator from agent to principal, in
OL,9,Fcontext with HMRC legislation it can
OL,10,Fhave "huge implications".
OL,12,FHe said operators or drivers with
OL,13,Ftotal annual fares of #90,000 or more
OL,14,Fwill have to charge VAT on all
OL,15,Fbookings.
