OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,F"Many of the small operators do not
OL,7,Fhave the administration capability to
OL,8,Fbe able to handle the tax returns and
OL,9,FVAT returns that we're talking about,
OL,10,Fand as well as putting the price up,
OL,11,Fit has the potential to put small
OL,12,Foperators and drivers off the road,"
OL,13,Fhe said.
OL,15,FHe said the change could also mean
OL,16,Fhaving to stop cash payments and
OL,17,Ftelephone bookings in order to keep
OL,18,Fabreast of the numbers for tax and VAT.
