OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,F"As well as putting the price up
OL,7,Fpotentially by 20%, this change of
OL,8,Flegislation also has the potential to
OL,9,Frule out anybody who only has the cash
OL,10,Foption and then take those people,
OL,11,Fsuch as a elderly, those who are not
OL,12,Ftech savvy, those who are perhaps
OL,13,Fblind or disabled, and can't use a web
OL,14,Fplatform, stops them from using
OL,15,Fservices as well," he said.
