OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,F"Should the legislation be approved,
OL,7,Fthe industry will adapt and the larger
OL,8,Foperators will survive. They will
OL,9,Fcollect the VAT for HMRC with the
OL,10,Fadditional costs for doing so, but
OL,11,Fthere will be hugely increased costs
OL,12,Ffor the public."
OL,14,FMr Anton also urged the committee to
OL,15,Fback a review of the sector.
