OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FCathy Mallie from Clanrye Taxis in
OL,7,FNewry said firms in rural areas are
OL,8,Fstruggling, having not recovered from
OL,9,Fthe pandemic, and having trouble
OL,10,Fsecuring drivers because of the
OL,11,Fdemands on qualifying.
OL,13,FShe said her firm "financially
OL,14,Fcouldn't afford" the administration
OL,15,Fthat would come with the legislative
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,18,F"We wouldn't have the finances. We're
OL,19,Freally struggling and we're really at
OL,20,Fdire straits at this stage," she said.
