OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,FAlso appearing before the committee
OL,7,Fwas Gerry Lennon, chief executive of
OL,8,FVisit Belfast, who voiced concern
OL,9,Faround the number of taxis in terms of
OL,10,Fbeing able to cater for tourism, which
OL,11,Fhe said is recovering since the
OL,12,Fpandemic.
OL,14,FHe said in the last year Belfast
OL,15,Fwelcomed 150 cruise ships and 325,000
OL,16,Fvisitors, 92 conferences, 32,000
OL,17,Fconference delegates and 390,000
OL,18,Fleisure bed nights.
