OL,3,CActive taxi driver numbers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland drop to 5,719 amid VAT fears
OL,6,F"A large proportion of those people
OL,7,Fneed taxi services, and the number of
OL,8,Ftaxi licences and taxi drivers is
OL,9,Fdecreasing as demand for this service
OL,10,Fis increasing," he told the committee.
OL,12,F"We are starting to get some feedback
OL,13,Ffrom visitors that there is
OL,14,Ffrustration around queues at cruise
OL,15,Fterminals and at airports, and that
OL,16,Fleads to a reputational issue that is
OL,17,Fgoing to be counterintuitive if we are
OL,18,Ftrying to grow the numbers we are
OL,19,Fexpecting."
